<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1914-07-23T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1914-07-23T00:00:00-05:00" n="1793" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1793">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 891.001/30.</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">President</gloss> to the
                                    <persName type="to">Shah</persName>.</hi>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                        </opener>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">The White House</hi>, <lb/>
                                    <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1914-07-23">
                                    <hi rend="italic">July 23, 1914</hi></date>.</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>On this felicitous occasion of the accession of Your Majesty to the
                            throne of Persia I extend to you the earnest hope that your beneficent
                            reign will mark an era of great prosperity and offer to Your Majesty the
                            assurances of my highest regards and good wishes.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Woodrow Wilson</hi></signed>.</closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>